            <title>search</title>

    <!DOCTYPE html>

    <!-- Demonstrates onsubmit -->

    <html lang="en">
        <head>
            <script>

                function greet()
                {
                    alert('hello, ' + document.querySelector('#name').value);
                }

            </script>
            <title>hello</title>
        </head>
        <body>
            <form onsubmit="greet(); return false;">
                <input autocomplete="off" autofocus id="name" placeholder="Name" type="text">
                <input type="submit">
            </form>
        </body>
    </html>
